import React from 'react'; import './Navbar.css'; export default function Navbar(props) { const { changeActiveTab } = props; const handleTabClick = (event, tabName) => { event.preventDefault(); changeActiveTab(tabName); }; return (
handleTabClick(event, 'home')}> {/* Your brand content */}
